title: Allman Brothers Band Ft. Zakk Wylde - Shredding The Great Woods
description:
Allman Brothers Band Ft. Zakk Wylde - Shredding The Great Woods 1993 ak

“On August 1, 1993, the Allman brothers Band had a scheduled gig at Great Woods in Mansfield, Massachusetts. Unfortunately, [guitarist] Dickie Betts was AWOL ... . The Allmans' first alternates, David Grissom and Jack Pearson, were both booked on the night elsewhere and unavailable, so Zakk got the call!”

So gather around and listen to a young Zakk Wylde play “Whipping Post” and many others with the 1993 version of the Allman Brothers Band, which also featured Warren Haynes. 
So gather around and listen to Zakk shredding The Great Woods
